{"word":"στοναχέω","slug":"στοναχέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>στοναχέω</b></el> <el>(στονᾰχέω,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>like <a href='S:στενάχω'><el>στενάχω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to groan, sigh</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:transitive'>trans.</a> <i>to sigh, groan over</i> or <i>for</i>, <el>τινά</el> <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Moschus'>Mosch.</a></b><p/></div><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <el>στονᾰχή</el>\n"}]}